{"tid":626940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咁有自信既金毛仔","createTime":"2018-04-12T14:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T16:04:57.000Z","uid":87154,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d95b7bb3dd0e4a48cb905b07e0cb390f8550e07","tid":626940,"uid":87154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"今日聽到有個後生仔話自己一出黎做野就2萬幾<br />\n家陣點高點高 過2萬 自信爆棚 <br />\n屌你老尾一望 金毛仔 再望到好似係地盤工人黎<br />\n做地盤搵命博先過2萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得淡笑 你見到呢個post 再望下個天空<br />\n人外有人 天外有天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣 做既行為成個乞衣咁 又瘦<br />\n地盤打雜都有2萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當正自己巴撚閉 金毛仔 聽日有冇工開都未知口口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86503411800471cd81dfcccd695355249fb5a184","tid":626940,"uid":87154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462e2547f95c1db1b5468e08f579f3034575bf3b","tid":626940,"uid":52814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"做乜唔係佢面前同佢講？"},{"pid":"16670617d9d89c66f8fd7f87b9d30f0fb8a4c93b","tid":626940,"uid":77461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"一出黎做野搵二萬幾好失禮？"},{"pid":"3d68b912c1c6bed8aca195e2c9d1c5e1044db6d8","tid":626940,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16670617d9d89c66f8fd7f87b9d30f0fb8a4c93b","tid":626940,"uid":77461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"一出黎做野搵二萬幾好失禮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"呢到啲人個個出黎40k up架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問埋啲咁既野 你傻左啊？"},{"pid":"5ebaf8571b2fe052ec6a09654497efa70aa01587","tid":626940,"uid":77716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16670617d9d89c